{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was just a one-night stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, I cannot run this risk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And three people, imagine, and there's my father without the uniform again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a primary problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other problem is, if you got stopped and you just said, I don't have my papers, but I'm a soldier on furlough, which he did later on for a time, if they're suspicious of you all they had to say was, drop your pants.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Remember that German people in those decades were not circumcised.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was a clear identification, a clear way for people-- for men to run into problems.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember that Hildegard Arnold took me home with her that-- at that time right from the first meeting so that they wouldn't have to worry about lugging a small child around.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right then and there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no thought.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you look at your parent, and if your parent says, you go with this nice Aunt Hilde, hey, you trust that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, my husband has said to this day he's never met anyone more trusting than I am.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How can it be that I lived through these events, all of them, and I'm so trusting that it's almost childish?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's almost a childish trust.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to believe in something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you went with--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went with Aunt Hilde, Tante Hilde, who happened to have a very nice, gentle, soft-spoken personality, never had children of her own.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a year younger than my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Took me to her very nice apartment, which was financed by her dad who was a high-ranking Nazi.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
